{"tid":762930,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"講到尾，Trump有三張牌","createTime":"2018-07-31T16:33:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-01T15:51:24.000Z","uid":73915,"like":37,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4fe539ef292a5be1ec43bda0bcef5d703169da8e","tid":762930,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T16:33:21.000Z","msg":"第一張：現代化農業（足以餓撚死支那人）<br />\n第二張：電腦技術（現代鴉片，社會現代化必須）<br />\n第三張：軍備（夷平支那）<br />\n<br />\n拖越耐，對中國越有利（總有一日會抄到）<br />\n只能暴力（武力或非武力）解決支那，因為支那係欺騙民族，任何條約都係垃圾"},{"pid":"d6d003d3714e7053f5e32143cdc6751e845f6db9","tid":762930,"uid":73915,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T16:42:12.000Z","msg":"Trump都係無謂講數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad184af2a71c7699b278d1d18007ac9ca66907c9","tid":762930,"uid":173397,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T16:42:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"15ea507802b1a5753195ca76e9aff83da780feaf","tid":762930,"uid":17859,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"ad184af2a71c7699b278d1d18007ac9ca66907c9","tid":762930,"uid":173397,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T16:42:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T16:44:14.000Z","msg":"2025中蟈製造又真係幾天真<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34a05323c9b4c6dcc37596f8d712dfebf42ca9fc","tid":762930,"uid":30169,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"15ea507802b1a5753195ca76e9aff83da780feaf","tid":762930,"uid":17859,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"ad184af2a71c7699b278d1d18007ac9ca66907c9","tid":762930,"uid":173397,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T16:42:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T16:44:14.000Z","msg":"2025中蟈製造又真係幾天真<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T16:45:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/01/004525_0eef4cf9720d22c597716eb5d81f109c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F01%2F004525_0eef4cf9720d22c597716eb5d81f109c.png&h=330b34c8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8f399b6cfb87218bbbdbb752a22b8f5c418ca07e","tid":762930,"uid":12994,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T16:48:30.000Z","msg":"終有一日 即係幾時？<br />\n中國終有一日起到艦隊<br />\n美國到時會唔會玩緊飛船？<br />\n<br />\n終有一日 其實係個希望黎<br />\n同埋一個國家 講緊十幾億人<br />\n咁易打理？ 中國跟本表面齊心<br />\n你睇班書記 黨主席 全部都係拎外國護照<br />\n一有咩姨郁個個都走<br />\n再早前 禁走資<br />\n然後講最基本 自給自足 同 日常生活既必需品<br />\n連魚都可以捉到無晒 毒奶粉 毒液苖<br />\n我都唔知你講既終有一日會係幾時"},{"pid":"3fe9e85b2676e31b6eb139dec9393e1c3e9fca0d","tid":762930,"uid":77803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T16:49:09.000Z","msg":"中共深耕細作左咁多年，咁多間諜，要抄真係會抄到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0b006c476283e35264fd4815a20a318aac5271f","tid":762930,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T16:49:27.000Z","msg":"on9 post<br />\ntrump最多咪做多10年8年 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n終有一日"},{"pid":"50b9d2e0fcdedd91a30266cd9fdda3f68b1d16bc","tid":762930,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3fe9e85b2676e31b6eb139dec9393e1c3e9fca0d","tid":762930,"uid":77803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T16:49:09.000Z","msg":"中共深耕細作左咁多年，咁多間諜，要抄真係會抄到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T16:53:19.000Z","msg":"係，好撚狗"},{"pid":"8234d884fae2aec43f094cb2d94c437c4dcfed13","tid":762930,"uid":36454,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T18:08:35.000Z","msg":"出兵要有媒體慢慢洗腦，或者911果啲事件，先爭取到民眾支持<br />\n<br />\n有咪依郁會比左膠圍屌，乃下下之策<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而貿易戰會直接沖戰支那經濟<br />\n<br />\n衰到一個點會逼支那開放市場，互聯網<br />\n<br />\n當支那人可以自由咁享受到優質既歐美貨<br />\n<br />\n就好似鴉片咁，慢慢上癮，變得依賴美貨，拖死內需<br />\n<br />\n乖乖輸出美金，最後一貧如洗，潦倒一世"},{"pid":"a7706ce3ebd30bd4ae39969b5727e6c4f8ca8000","tid":762930,"uid":41245,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8234d884fae2aec43f094cb2d94c437c4dcfed13","tid":762930,"uid":36454,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T18:08:35.000Z","msg":"出兵要有媒體慢慢洗腦，或者911果啲事件，先爭取到民眾支持<br />\n<br />\n有咪依郁會比左膠圍屌，乃下下之策<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而貿易戰會直接沖戰支那經濟<br />\n<br />\n衰到一個點會逼支那開放市場，互聯網<br />\n<br />\n當支那人可以自由咁享受到優質既歐美貨<br />\n<br />\n就好似鴉片咁，慢慢上癮，變得依賴美貨，拖死內需<br />\n<br />\n乖乖輸出美金，最後一貧如洗，潦倒一世"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T21:13:56.000Z","msg":"支那開放市場嘅話啲外匯一下冇晒啦<br />\n依家個泡沫係基於貿易順差<br />\n企業靠依啲貿易優勢去做借貸<br />\n一冇咗貿易順差 一大堆公司撐唔住<br />\n公司撐唔住就搞到市民收入<br />\n市民冇錢連內需又推唔到<br />\n根本支那就太天真樂觀<br />\n以為可以靠美國順差一直落去"},{"pid":"763d2595f4bce13ce08740a6e94253ed94990ca7","tid":762930,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad184af2a71c7699b278d1d18007ac9ca66907c9","tid":762930,"uid":173397,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T16:42:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T21:14:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">2025呢？</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">2025呢？</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">2025呢？</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">2025呢？</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2025呢？</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2025呢？</span>"},{"pid":"e9b209a8f2d395e0f00f5d59ff6a7a011501ecb6","tid":762930,"uid":4575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T22:03:40.000Z","msg":"超！我地習大大有4副棋"},{"pid":"569dc999043d0cee432892c5fb230924cd353bc7","tid":762930,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T00:23:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d2293dee34e8a85deef22382ea16599f938237e7","tid":762930,"uid":73915,"li